Alchemy Seeks Bank to Lead Revolution Vodka Bar Sale, Mail Says

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-10-16T13:48:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/alchemy-seeks-bank-to-lead-revolution-vodka-bar-sale-mail-says.html
Alchemy Partners LLP, a London-based
private-equity company, plans to put its Revolution chain of
vodka bars up for sale early next year, the Mail on Sunday
reported without saying where it got the information.  The company has asked bankers for proposals to manage the
sale, the London-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London at 
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
